current.name: Multibond 35-S - S GREY-290
current.description: Soudal Multibond 35 S - S GREY 290 is an adhesive and high-quality, permanently flexible joint sealant based on SMX Polymer and with a "Shore A" hardness of 35 (allowing accommodation of movement in joints). It is suitable for internal and external applications while bonding to a wide range of substrate forming a strong, flexible, and waterproof seal. It comes in a 290ml cartridge in Concrete Grey or Dark Grey color.
